product_name: Cycle Dog Trail Buddy Dog Treats
long_description: Made and sourced in the USA, the Cycle Dog Trail Buddy 100% Meat Treats give your pooch a protein-rich boost on the trail or a treat for good behavior at home. Choose from 100% lamb, beef or chicken; contains no grains, additives or other ingredients. Made and sourced in the USA. Each packet contains 2 oz. of meat treats.
